Privacy Policy for Flashlight

Effective Date: 01/01/2023

Thank you for using Flashlight. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information about you when you use our mobile application (the "App").

Information We Collect

We collect information about you when you use our App. This includes:

Analytics data: We collect anonymous data about how you use the App, such as which features you use and how often you use them. This information helps us improve the App and provide you with better service.

Advertising data: We work with third-party advertising partners to show you ads in the App. These partners may collect information about your device and your interaction with their ads to provide you with more relevant advertising. For more information about how these partners use your information, please see their privacy policies.

Device information: We collect information about your device, including its operating system, hardware, and software versions, and unique device identifiers. This information helps us diagnose technical issues and provide you with better service.

Location information: We may collect information about your location to provide you with location-based services, such as local weather information or personalized recommendations. If you do not want us to collect this information, you can turn off location services for the App in your device settings.

Use of Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide and improve the App: We use analytics data to understand how you use the App and to improve its features and functionality. We use advertising data to show you relevant ads in the App.

Personalize your experience: We may use your location information to provide you with personalized content and recommendations.

Communicate with you: We may use your information to send you updates about the App or to respond to your inquiries and requests.

Disclosure of Information

We may disclose the information we collect to third parties, including:

Service providers: We may share your information with service providers who help us operate and improve the App.

Advertising partners: We may share your information with third-party advertising partners who show you ads in the App.

Legal authorities: We may disclose your information to law enforcement authorities or other government officials if required by law or if we believe in good faith that such disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, your safety, or the safety of others.

Updates to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or to comply with legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes to this Privacy Policy by posting a notice in the App or by sending you an email.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at a13software.development@gmail.com.
